      "rationale": "Testing was conducted under a single ASTM F1717 standard configuration (35 mm inter-body distance, 10° angulation). While this configuration is the regulatory standard, it represents only one point in the clinical loading space. No additional test conditions (e.g., varied inter-body distance, angulation, or dynamic loading) were evaluated. Achieved level 1 is below the required level 2; this known gap is accepted by the credibility assessment team given the regulatory context where ASTM F1717 single-condition testing is the established standard."
    },
