      "rationale": "Fixture geometry, loading rate (5 mm/min quasi-static), specimen alignment, and boundary conditions in the FEA models were set to match the experimental test setup as documented in the test protocol (TP-F1717-NC-001). Fixture compliance was measured experimentally and incorporated into the FEA boundary conditions. Residual discrepancies in fixture stiffness were estimated to contribute less than 0.3% to QoI difference."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Output comparison",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
